<h1 class='article-card__title'>
Identifying Einstein
</h1>
<h2 class='article-card__standfirst'>
For Albert Einstein, being Jewish and German were not questions of identity but rather mutable matters of identification
</h2>
<p class='article-card__authors'>
<span class='article-card__authors__inner'>Michael D Gordin</span>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>

</div>
<div class='article__image__caption container' data-caption-align='right'>
<div class='column'>
<div class='gutter'><p>Albert Einstein's original passport. <em>Photo by Jean-Pierre Clatot/AFP/Getty</em></p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='article__wrapper'>
<div class='article article--society container essay' id='essay_3651'>
